News.headline: 50/50 Draw York City
News.short_description: The winner for the Daggers' Vanarama National League game versus York City is ticket number 06597
News.description:
The winning ticket worth £156.50 was drawn at half time. The winning ticket has yet to be claimed.

Second place winner for the £50 Johnstone's Paint voucher is ticket number 06645, this ticket is also yet to be claimed.

50/50 tickets can be purchased on match days for £1.
